description:
Kari Lake on why she wants to be Arizona governor. Biden regime wants return to "version of normalcy." Can somebody tell us if LeBron James faked a hate crime? LAPD investigated LeBron's 2017 claim that his gate was vandalized, found no evidence a crime was committed, media dropped story. C&B tale Open Line Friday calls.
